At\
the\
turn\
of\
2008,\
the\
media\
started\
reporting\
that\
the\
Kosovo\
Albanians\
were\
determined\
to\
proclaim\
independence.\
This\
came\
at\
the\
time\
when\
the\
ten-year\
anniversary\
of\
the\
Kosovo\
War\
was\
looming\
(with\
the\
five-year\
anniversary\
being\
marked\
